  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Required_resource_arm.Required_resource">
A <b>Required_resource</b> is a  representation of resources needed in order to achieve a specified objective. The role of a required resource is determined by classification.
<example number="1">
 "Facility", "Test equipment", "Supervisor" are examples of classifications of a required resource.</example>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
